# Adversarial Plan Review Projection

## Purpose

This projection defines the project-specific attack surface for adversarial plan review.

It exists to help AdversarialPlanReview identify how a plan could silently diverge from this project’s Project Context while appearing coherent, executable, or complete.

It is a projection of the Project Context, not a plan review, execution plan, milestone spec, implementation guide, or generic review rubric.

## Authority Boundary

- The Project Context remains the source of authority.
- This projection is a task-specific adversarial review view of the Project Context.
- This projection defines project-specific attack surfaces.
- This projection does not review any plan.
- This projection does not define generic severity rules.
- This projection does not define the downstream output format.
- This projection does not generate patches.
- This projection does not include implementation tasks.
- This projection does not modify plan, epic, roadmap, or operational context.

